  "text": "Primary studies on how to apply IEEE 802.16j multi-hop relays to the AeroMACS prototype to enhance its capacity and flexibility are discussed in [CITATION_1] - [CITATION_2] . The proposed method increases the ground station capacity and provides the transmitters with transparent and non-transparent relay modes. This technique reduces the interference.",
